Sven (15) is a director and has been busy filming. He films his friends who mostly do free running and put the videos on YouTube. He asks Lilly Pulitzer to work on his first feature film. They may not know that he gets a thrashing at home regularly. He manages his bruises hidden from everyone until he one day so badly that he absconds with his grandmother. Thus he misses his birthday. Lilly Pulitzer thinks he does not like her and his friends are angry with him. He decides once and for all with his father to settle, until he discovered why his father beats him.

